{"tid":2398163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傑斯叔剛遭香港警惡魔綁架","createTime":"2021-02-07T05:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T07:20:00.000Z","uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bae2258030b468bbaabbc33df8f5964ca7403abd","tid":2398163,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:13:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210207/L3W6KRCY6FHVNGEW4XYCWD25VY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210207%2FL3W6KRCY6FHVNGEW4XYCWD25VY%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=fc8a85ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210207%2FL3W6KRCY6FHVNGEW4XYCWD25VY%2F&h=ca9e2299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210207/L3W6KRCY6FHVNGEW4XYCWD25VY/</a><br />\n<br />\n網台主持傑斯<del>再被捕 </del>被指涉嫌作出具煽動意圖的作為<br />\n<br />\nD100網台主持傑斯去年初於網上發起眾籌，卻遭警方指控洗黑錢，傑斯、其妻子及女助理去年底涉嫌「洗黑錢」及「資助分裂國家」被捕。警方今日發新聞稿指，國安處經進一步調查後，今日在港島區拘捕傑斯（52歲），涉嫌「作出具煽動意圖的作為」罪，違反香港法例第200章《刑事罪行條例》第10 條。<br />\n<br />\n網台主持傑斯原名尹耀昇，是本港網台界第一代主持人之一。去年11月傑斯與姓曾妻子在北角被警察上門拘捕，傑斯一名姓利女助理亦被捕。警方拘捕行動的關鍵，涉及<span class=\"red\">傑斯去年2月在網上提出名為「千個爸媽，台灣助學」計劃</span>，希望集合1,000個家長眾籌，每人每年捐款約2,500元，協助受社會運動影響的港青在台灣讀書，包括協助應付學費及生活費，甚至尋找寄宿家庭。同月《文匯報》曾撰文炮轟傑斯，涉抹黑該計劃為「助養潛逃到台的黑魔」。據悉警方因此展開調查。"},{"pid":"aa58c7d77be6cda548cadd622e32e3deb443dcb7","tid":2398163,"uid":26770,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"「千個爸媽，台灣助學」就係幫緊流亡台灣班小朋友<br />\n<br />\n香港警魔唔止強姦,殺人<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">連流亡的小朋友都唔放過</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">記住香港警魔的父母子女都係邪魔,無一個值得同情</span>"},{"pid":"e99488c1c07a835c8a73cfd4f89abd78a148ccad","tid":2398163,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5285ec3321048e335a8f893a547b3edfaa9fc2","tid":2398163,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212f6390870a34c9a1d7cbd039525ee34a07a4f7","tid":2398163,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989bdd6d0ca8521ef19220e40606b40b5df3932b","tid":2398163,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9cc2ce2d3ae28d81fafcc414370dc654c7e03a","tid":2398163,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbe5a1050c68d9e2953a3f8cf609d66ffcdf97f","tid":2398163,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390d0dcaf0beeff1ce8511a37e5e368c0c8dbf29","tid":2398163,"uid":135008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"8c9ddcf9aabe57ad8b78818507ec8646364cccaf","tid":2398163,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:32:25.000Z","msg":"睇清事實未<br />\n<br />\n捨得走未<br />\n<br />\n連登傻鳩留港撚"},{"pid":"67677519bab97630e6b09fcd1362d7713bb892ab","tid":2398163,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c9ddcf9aabe57ad8b78818507ec8646364cccaf","tid":2398163,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:32:25.000Z","msg":"睇清事實未<br />\n<br />\n捨得走未<br />\n<br />\n連登傻鳩留港撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">不論離開定堅守都係手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span> </span><br />\n<br />\n決意堅守陣地既手足，必須時刻警惕提防，保留有用之軀，日後方能煲底相見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我認為中共已撕破臉皮，唔會再講法理情，只餘硬碰硬一著，而港共武裝與抗爭者實力相距太大，難成氣候，除非把抗爭層面擴大化，將火魔、簡易組裝槍械等等變成家家戶戶都有的必備品，否則難以對抗如同送頭，亦無必要，而且傳播該類資訊卻係十分頭痛既議題，能參與者的數量亦成疑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"> <span class=\"red\">今次 BNO 大量港人走資走人逼中共支爆發難，借東風，引天下圍中，百國聯軍，打柒老共，核平北京！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>所以：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"> <span class=\"red\">離開唔係逃避，係主動攬炒救香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>警號已經響起咗！越著時間過去，離開香港將會日漸困難，大時代中不能存有饒幸之心，成日同自己講冇事既、冇事既個d人，就係走唔切，困咗係東德既人。<span class=\"red\">總之任何人，有得即走，特別高風險人士一定要最早走，其他人遲極唔可以遲過外國撤僑，外國第一個國家撤僑你就要跟住飛。外國唔會一次過撤，會比時間同signal香港人走先。</span>切記你係難民唔係移民。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪好好奇美國點解得把口唔出手制裁？我話你知幾時先制裁、有冇可能封關、應唔應該走、幾時要走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2093986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2093986</a><br />\n<br />\n(分析)仲有幾耐入東突(新疆)模式，見到咩警告要流亡？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1980175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1980175</a><br />\n<br />\n香港簡易流亡手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/478029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/478029</a><br />\n<br />\n[借古鑑今] 中國因逃亡潮於 1951 年 2 月 15 日鎖關，香港因 BNO 鎖關的憂慮正響歐美之間蔓延！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390806</a>"},{"pid":"0a413c461fe5b20aa804345f31c1a53a2c06d8e3","tid":2398163,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67677519bab97630e6b09fcd1362d7713bb892ab","tid":2398163,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c9ddcf9aabe57ad8b78818507ec8646364cccaf","tid":2398163,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime